data.description: Welcome to 4524 Price Rd, a charming single-family home located in Gainesville, GA. This beautiful home was built in 1979 and boasts a timeless design of wood tones that exudes warmth and character. Situated on a spacious lot spanning 2+/- acres with a recent survey, this property offers plenty of room to enjoy outdoor activities and create your own private oasis. With a total of 3 bedrooms, including 2 full bathrooms and 1 half bathroom, this home offers convenience and comfort for you and your family. Home also has an office that could be converted into a 4th bedroom. The finished area of the home spans 2,100+/- square feet, providing ample space for living, dining, and entertaining. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a cozy living room filled with natural light and featuring a fireplace, creating a welcoming atmosphere for relaxing or gathering with loved ones. Massive kitchen is well-appointed with plenty of cabinet storage, counter top space, modern appliances, making meal prep and cooking a breeze and a cozy coffee sitting area. The bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of closet space for storage. The bathrooms are tastefully designed with updated fixtures and finishings. House features 1000 +/- sq ft garage that has a new HVAC system that includes a 10 year warranty. Property features a fully functional and self contained tiny home. (negotiable with offer) Outside, the expansive lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Whether you're looking to create a lush garden, set up a play area for kids, or simply relax and enjoy the fresh air, this property has the space to accommodate all your outdoor needs to include a new covered 26x12 rv/boat parking/storage area. Conveniently located in Gainesville, GA, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, schools, and entertainment options in Gainesville, Dawsonville, and Dahlonega. With its timeless design, spacious lot, and convenient location, 4524 Price Rd is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss your chance to make this property your own and start enjoying the comfort and convenience it has to offer. Schedule a showing today!.
